(692, 1, '2021-11-02 15:17:50', '2021-11-02 15:17:50', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Vi 10 ng dng v bn di y, bn c th tr thnh ha s chuyn nghip  sng to nn hng lot nhng tc</strong> <strong>phm  ha ngh thut vi b cng c phong ph, ti u. Hy theo di v la chn cho mnh mt ng dng ph hp nh!</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Procreate</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":693,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://nhom08inurarea.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/proct.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-693\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Procreate c bit n l mt trong nhng ng dng minh ha chuyn nghip, sng to v trc quan nht hin nay trn iPad dnh cho cc ngh s sng to. Ngay c nhng ha s, concept artist, designer t cc hng phim, studio, game ni ting nh Pixar Animation Studio, Disney, Mattel, Ubisoft, DC Comicscng rt a chung ng dng ny. Procreate cng l ng dng  tng ot gii thng Apple Design Award v App Store Essential.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Vi Procreate, ngi dng s c c hi tri nghim rt nhiu tnh nng phc ha t ph nh ty chnh  phn gii canvas, 128 mu bt v, layer tin tin, bng mu phong ph, cliping masksProcreate h tr to ra cc bc tranh sn du (canvas) c  phn gii cao n kh tin cha tng c  ng dng no trn thit b cm ng. Nh , ngi dng d dng in c tc phm ngh thut ca mnh  kch thc ln. Hn na, ng dng cn c giao din c thit k trc quan, hin i v lun t yu t ngh thut ln hng u.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>SketchBook</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":696,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://nhom08inurarea.cc/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/SketchBook-App-Review-Appedus.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-696\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>ng dng v SketchBook hon ton min ph cho php cc nh thit k, kin trc s v ha s, v phc tho, trnh din  tng nhanh chng v to ra cc hnh minh ha tuyt p bt c lc no c cm hng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>u im ln ca cng c chuyn nghip ny chnh l giao din lm vic ton mn hnh p mt, l tng cho nhng ngi hay di chuyn. ng dng cn cung cp mt khng gian lm vic ti u  ngi dng thao tc v nhanh chng khi cn. Sketchbook s hu cc cng c c v (Brush) mnh nht trong App Store, vi 60 kiu c khc nhau, t bt ch, trn mm mi, vung, airbrush (bt ngh thut), bn thm ch c th la chn cc k hiu nh l cy, hoc hoa. Mi c v c th c ty chnh bng cch iu chnh bn knh,  m c ca n, lng, v khong cch.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt trong nhng th bn s kh tm thy trong bt k ng dng khc l cng c i xng ca Sketchbook. Khi cng c ny hot ng, mi khi bn thc hin v th t ng ton b hnh bn v c nhn i  pha bn kia ca mn hnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>Adobe Illustrator</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>n t nh pht hnh Adobe, Illustrator chnh l cng c v k thut s m bn khng nn b qua. Adobe Illustrator gip ngi dng to cc hnh nh minh ha di dng  ha vector mt cch cc k n tng, m ch dng nhng thao tc n gin nh chm v vut.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn c th s dng cc cy c c th ty chnh c  v, thit k v to phong cch cho tc phm ca mnh. Adobe Illustrator bao gm cc khun t (stencil) hnh dng c bn  bn y nhanh tc  thit k ca mnh nh hnh trn, vung, ng cong Php (French curve), hnh a gic v thm ch c bong bng tr chuyn  v truyn tranh. Ngoi ra, tc phm Illustrator ca bn s c t ng ng b ha vi m my, v vy bn lun c th truy cp phin bn mi nht t <a href=\"https://fptshop.com.vn/may-tinh-de-ban\">my tnh  bn</a>&nbsp;hoc iPad ca mnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Top 3 ng dng luyn v trn iPad hay nht hin nay', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'top-3-ung-dung-luyen-ve-tren-ipad-hay-nhat-hien-nay', '', '', '2021-11-02 15:18:32', '2021-11-02 15:18:32', '', 0, 'https://nhom08inurarea.cc/?p=692', 0, 'post', '', 0),
